commit.message: Added automake files compile and test-driver to .gitignore.
Added check-error script to check error behaviour.
Add verbose option to coveralls.
Added tests to increase coverage. Removed set but unused variables.
Enabled gcov coverage. Added coverage to README.
Added configure option --enable-gcov to enable gcov code coverage.
Modify README to use markdown.

Change the bug-report string in AC_INIT from the ipgen email address to the
github URL.
Corrected program name in --version output. Updated copyright year.

Removed $Id$ keywords from all files.
.gitignore: new file with patterns that shouldn't be committed to the
repository.
.travis.yml: new file to enable automatic building on Travis CI.

Final SVN commit before move to git on github.
